15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 37A O.S. 2021, Section 2-142, is
17 amended to read as follows:
18 Section 2-142. A. No license provided for in the Oklahoma
19 Alcoholic Beverage Control Act shall be issued except pursuant to an
20 application filed with the ABLE Commission. The ABLE Commission
21 may, however, provide for a form of simplified application for
22 renewal of a license. Payment of the prescribed fee shall accompany
23 each application for a license.
